Description: Mahjong
        -------
        
        Abstract away the logic of Mahjong games (for oh, it is complicated!)
        Only worry about the representation.
        
        Example Usage
        =============
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            >>> import mahjong
            >>> game = mahjong.Game()
            >>> question = game.play()
            >>> next_question = question.answer(...)
            >>> ...
        
        For full usage see the docs:
        https://github.com/Kenny2github/mahjong/wiki
